# Webapp (React/TypeScript)

## Registration (index.tsx)

```typescript
// RHS
const { showRHSPlugin, hideRHSPlugin } = registry.registerRightHandSidebarComponent(
    RHSSidebar, 'Solidtime',
);

// Channel Header — when server_url is configured (syncChrome)
registry.registerChannelHeaderButtonAction(
    icon, () => store.dispatch(showRHSPlugin), 'Solidtime', 'Open Solidtime Time Tracker',
);
```

```
webapp/src/components/
├── channel_header_button.tsx
└── rhs/
    ├── sidebar.tsx           # Layout: form + list + footer
    ├── connect_panel.tsx     # Connect screen (not connected)
    ├── time_entry_form.tsx
    ├── project_selector.tsx
    ├── tag_selector.tsx
    ├── time_entry_list.tsx
    └── pagination_footer.tsx  # position: sticky; bottom: 0
```

UI specification — `docs/UI.md`.

## API client

- All requests via `webapp/src/api/client.ts` to `/plugins/{manifest.id}/api/v1/`
- Use `getPluginRoute()` or equivalent from Mattermost webapp utilities
- **Never** store or send the Solidtime API token on the client

## State

- `connection/status` — on plugin initialization
- Form — local state; reset after successful ADD
- Entry list — reload after create; pagination in footer

## Styles

- Mattermost CSS variables: `--center-channel-bg`, `--button-bg`, `--online-indicator`
- Compact layout for narrow RHS (~400px)
